# smartcardfyi-rs — Rust API Client Demo
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1000
Set Height 580
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 24

Type "# SmartCardFYI Rust API Client"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s

Type "curl -s 'https://smartcardfyi.com/api/random/' | jq '{name, slug}'"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "curl -s 'https://smartcardfyi.com/api/term/apdu/' | jq '{name, definition}'"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 1s
